<DocsPageTitle Path="Components/Image">
    Blazorise Image component
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    The image component represents a visual component that, in addition to displaying the visual type of pixelated data, also contributes to the appearance of the same page.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    An <Code Tag>Image</Code> component is a visual representation of something, while a digital image is a binary representation of visual data. For this purpose, an image is a picture that was created or copied and stored in electronic form.
</DocsPageParagraph>

